   <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">This procedure applies to all Space employees, contractors and visitors, and all operations including standard and non-standard (i.e., construction projects) activities within manufacturing facilities, technical centers, offices, and administrative buildings where lifting activities may occur.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Requirements of this procedure will apply to the control of risks associated with lifting loads using lifting devices such as cranes, hoists, and winches. Specifically, this protocol relates to the risks associated with working in and around loads being lifted above the ground.</li>
